title: Mystery Temple of the Serpent Priest
story: After being destroyed by a great magic storm a long time ago the temple of the Serpent Priest remained abandoned. These days it is overrun with snakes, indifferent to the past of the place. Rumors say that a legendary grimoire Baran is still hidden here.

notes.text: A massive double door to the east.
A large chest holds a robe and a dagger.
A weird, sticky to touch helm among rubble on the ground.
A writing on the wall painted in blood: EMBRACE THE DEATH
